          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:28px">sailing</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-3">Kargo Laut</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant flex-grow">Pilihan ekonomis untuk kiriman berat dan volume besar dengan kapal cepat.</p>
        <span class="mt-6 font-label text-label-caps text-primary flex items-center gap-2 group-hover:gap-4 transition-all">
          LIHAT DETAIL <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">arrow_forward</span>
        </span>
      </a>
      <a href="/layanan/" class="group bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant p-8 flex flex-col hover:border-primary transition-all">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center bg-primary-fixed text-primary mb-6">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:28px">local_shipping</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-3">Kargo Darat</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant flex-grow">Layanan via truk &amp; ekspedisi darat antar pulau dan antar kota di seluruh Indonesia.</p>
        <span class="mt-6 font-label text-label-caps text-primary flex items-center gap-2 group-hover:gap-4 transition-all">
          LIHAT DETAIL <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">arrow_forward</span>
        </span>
      </a>
      <a href="/layanan/" class="group bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant p-8 flex flex-col hover:border-primary transition-all">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center bg-surface-container text-on-surface-variant mb-6">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:28px">inventory_2</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-3">Packing &amp; Kayu</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant flex-grow">Jasa pengemasan dan packing kayu profesional agar barang Anda lebih aman.</p>
        <span class="mt-6 font-label text-label-caps text-primary flex items-center gap-2 group-hover:gap-4 transition-all">
          LIHAT DETAIL <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">arrow_forward</span>
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Rute Populer -->
<section class="py-24 bg-surface-container-low px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <span class="font-label text-label-caps text-secondary mb-2 block tracking-widest uppercase">Rute Terpopuler</span>
      <h2 class="font-headline text-display-lg-mobile text-primary">Pengiriman dari Bandung</h2>
      <p class="font-body text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-4 max-w-lg mx-auto">
        Klik tujuan untuk melihat info lengkap, estimasi waktu, dan cara order.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center">
      {% set routes = [
        { href: "/kargo-pengiriman-bandung-banjarmasin/",            label: "Bandung → Banjarmasin" },
        { href: "/kirim-barang-bandung-balikpapan/",                 label: "Bandung → Balikpapan" },
        { href: "/pengiriman-bandung-ke-samarinda/",                  label: "Bandung → Samarinda" },
        { href: "/pengiriman-paket-bandung-pontianak-murah-cepat/",   label: "Bandung → Pontianak" },
        { href: "/ongkir-bandung-banjarbaru-murah/",                  label: "Bandung → Banjarbaru" },
        { href: "/kirim-paket-bandung-makassar-ongkir-murah/",        label: "Bandung → Makassar" },
        { href: "/pengiriman-bandung-palu/",                          label: "Bandung → Palu" },
        { href: "/pengiriman-bandung-kendari/",                       label: "Bandung → Kendari" },
        { href: "/pengiriman-bandung-manado/",                        label: "Bandung → Manado" },
        { href: "/pengiriman-bandung-palangkaraya/",                  label: "Bandung → Palangka Raya" },
        { href: "/pengiriman-bandung-tarakan/",                       label: "Bandung → Tarakan" },
        { href: "/kargo-bandung-jayapura/",                           label: "Bandung → Jayapura" },
        { href: "/kargo-bandung-sorong/",                             label: "Bandung → Sorong" },
        { href: "/kiriman-paket-dengan-ongkir-murah-bandung-ke-denpasar-bali/", label: "Bandung → Denpasar" }
      ] %}
      {% for route in routes %}
        <a href="{{ route.href }}"
           class="bg-surface border border-outline-variant px-4 py-2 font-body text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-all">
          {{ route.label }}
        </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="text-center mt-10">
      <a href="/tarif/" class="border border-primary text-primary px-8 py-3 font-bold text-body-md hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-2">
        Lihat Semua Kota Tujuan <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Keunggulan -->
<section class="py-24 bg-surface px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="font-label text-label-caps text-secondary mb-2 block tracking-widest uppercase">Mengapa Kami</span>
      <h2 class="font-headline text-display-lg-mobile text-primary">Kenapa Memilih Perdana Prima Express?</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-gutter">
      <div class="p-10 bg-surface-container-low border-b-4 border-secondary hover:bg-surface-container transition-all">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-6">verified_user</span>
        <h3 class="font-headline text-headline-md text-primary mb-4">Aman &amp; Terpercaya</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Barang ditangani profesional dari kantor cabang resmi di kota asal hingga tiba di tujuan.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-10 bg-surface-container-low border-b-4 border-secondary hover:bg-surface-container transition-all">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-6">payments</span>
        <h3 class="font-headline text-headline-md text-primary mb-4">Ongkir Bersaing</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Tarif kompetitif untuk pengiriman ke Kalimantan, Sulawesi, Bali, dan Papua dengan layanan terbaik.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-10 bg-surface-container-low border-b-4 border-secondary hover:bg-surface-container transition-all">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-6">route</span>
        <h3 class="font-headline text-headline-md text-primary mb-4">Armada Sendiri</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Didukung armada milik sendiri dan pengalaman bertahun-tahun di bidang ekspedisi nusantara.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-10 bg-surface-container-low border-b-4 border-secondary hover:bg-surface-container transition-all">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-6">location_on</span>
        <h3 class="font-headline text-headline-md text-primary mb-4">Jangkauan Luas</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Melayani 200+ kota &amp; kabupaten di seluruh Indonesia dari 3 kantor cabang strategis.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-10 bg-surface-container-low border-b-4 border-secondary hover:bg-surface-container transition-all">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-6">bolt</span>
        <h3 class="font-headline text-headline-md text-primary mb-4">Proses Cepat</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Pemesanan mudah lewat WhatsApp, respon cepat, jadwal pengiriman rutin setiap hari.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-10 bg-surface-container-low border-b-4 border-secondary hover:bg-surface-container transition-all">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-6">support_agent</span>
        <h3 class="font-headline text-headline-md text-primary mb-4">Layanan Personal</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Tim kami siap membantu konsultasi jenis pengiriman yang paling sesuai dengan kebutuhan Anda.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Cara Kirim -->
<section class="py-24 bg-surface-container-low px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="font-label text-label-caps text-secondary mb-2 block tracking-widest uppercase">Mudah &amp; Cepat</span>
      <h2 class="font-headline text-display-lg-mobile text-primary">Cara Kirim Barang Bersama Kami</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-gutter">
      {% set steps = [
        { n: "1", icon: "chat",             title: "Hubungi Kami",    desc: "Chat WhatsApp untuk konsultasi &amp; cek tarif pengiriman." },
        { n: "2", icon: "send_to_mobile",   title: "Kirim / Pickup",  desc: "Antar ke cabang atau minta penjemputan barang di lokasi Anda." },
        { n: "3", icon: "inventory_2",      title: "Packing",         desc: "Barang dikemas aman, packing kayu tersedia bila diperlukan." },
        { n: "4", icon: "check_circle",     title: "Terkirim",        desc: "Barang dikirim dan sampai di kota tujuan dengan selamat." }
      ] %}
      {% for step in steps %}
      <div class="bg-surface p-8 border border-outline-variant text-center flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary text-on-primary flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg mb-6">{{ step.n }}</div>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl mb-4">{{ step.icon }}</span>
        <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-3">{{ step.title }}</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">{{ step.desc }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Cabang -->
<section class="py-24 bg-surface px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="font-label text-label-caps text-secondary mb-2 block tracking-widest uppercase">Lokasi Kami</span>
      <h2 class="font-headline text-display-lg-mobile text-primary">Kantor Cabang</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-gutter">
      {% for branch in site.branches %}
      <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant p-8 flex flex-col">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl mb-4">store</span>
        <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-3">{{ branch.city }}</h3>
        <address class="font-body text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant not-italic mb-6 flex-grow">{{ branch.address }}</address>
        <a href="https://wa.me/{{ site.wa[branch.waKey].number }}?text={{ site.wa[branch.waKey].text }}"
           class="bg-[#25D366] text-white px-6 py-3 font-bold text-body-sm flex items-center justify-center gap-2 hover:bg-[#1fbe5c] transition-colors">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0"><path d="M16 .4C7.4.4.5 7.3.5 15.9c0 2.8.7 5.5 2.1 7.9L.3 31.6l8-2.1c2.3 1.3 4.9 1.9 7.6 1.9 8.6 0 15.5-6.9 15.5-15.5C31.5 7.3 24.6.4 16 .4zm0 28.4c-2.4 0-4.7-.6-6.7-1.9l-.5-.3-4.8 1.3 1.3-4.7-.3-.5c-1.4-2.1-2.1-4.6-2.1-7.1C2.9 8.6 8.8 2.8 16 2.8c7.2 0 13.1 5.9 13.1 13.1 0 7.2-5.9 12.9-13.1 12.9zm7.2-9.6c-.4-.2-2.3-1.1-2.7-1.3-.4-.1-.6-.2-.9.2-.3.4-1 1.3-1.2 1.5-.2.2-.4.3-.8.1-.4-.2-1.7-.6-3.2-2-1.2-1.1-2-2.4-2.2-2.8-.2-.4 0-.6.2-.8.2-.2.4-.4.6-.7.2-.2.3-.4.4-.7.1-.3 0-.5 0-.7-.1-.2-.9-2.2-1.3-3-.3-.8-.6-.7-.9-.7h-.7c-.2 0-.6.1-1 .5-.3.4-1.3 1.3-1.3 3.1 0 1.8 1.3 3.6 1.5 3.8.2.2 2.6 4 6.3 5.6.9.4 1.6.6 2.1.8.9.3 1.7.2 2.3.1.7-.1 2.3-.9 2.6-1.8.3-.9.3-1.6.2-1.8-.1-.2-.3-.3-.7-.5z"/></svg>
          WA {{ site.wa[branch.waKey].label }}
        </a>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="py-24 bg-surface-container-low px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="font-label text-label-caps text-secondary mb-2 block tracking-widest uppercase">FAQ</span>
      <h2 class="font-headline text-display-lg-mobile text-primary">Pertanyaan yang Sering Diajukan</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      {% set faqs = [
        { q: "Apa saja layanan Perdana Prima Express?",
          a: "Kami melayani pengiriman barang, paket, dan kargo via udara, laut, dan darat ke seluruh Indonesia, termasuk pengiriman kendaraan/motor, barang cair, serta jasa packing kayu." },
        { q: "Dari kota mana saja Perdana Prima Express melayani pengiriman?",
          a: "Kami memiliki kantor cabang di Bandung, Jakarta, dan Surabaya, dengan tujuan utama ke Kalimantan, Sulawesi, Bali, dan Papua." },
        { q: "Bagaimana cara mengetahui ongkos kirim?",
          a: "Hubungi kami melalui WhatsApp 0821-30-2000-30 atau lihat halaman Tarif. Ongkir dihitung berdasarkan berat aktual atau berat volume (mana yang lebih besar) dan kota tujuan." },
        { q: "Apakah barang saya aman selama pengiriman?",
          a: "Ya. Perdana Prima Express memiliki armada sendiri dan kantor cabang resmi di kota asal pengiriman sehingga barang Anda tertangani secara profesional." }
      ] %}
      {% for faq in faqs %}
      <details class="bg-surface border border-outline-variant group">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-5 cursor-pointer font-headline font-semibold text-primary list-none">
          {{ faq.q }}
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">expand_more</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-5 font-body text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">{{ faq.a }}</div>
      </details>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="bg-primary text-on-primary py-24 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute -right-24 -bottom-24 w-96 h-96 bg-primary-container rounded-full opacity-20 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
    <h2 class="font-display text-display-lg-mobile md:text-display-lg mb-6">Siap Mengirim Barang Anda?</h2>
    <p class="font-body text-body-lg text-on-primary-container mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Konsultasi gratis dan dapatkan penawaran ongkir terbaik sekarang juga.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="https://wa.me/{{ site.wa.bandung.number }}?text={{ site.wa.bandung.text }}"
         class="bg-surface text-primary px-12 py-4 font-bold text-body-md flex items-center justify-center gap-2 hover:bg-surface-container transition-all">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">chat</span>
        Chat WhatsApp Sekarang
      </a>
      <a href="/tarif/"
         class="border border-on-primary text-on-primary px-12 py-4 font-bold text-body-md flex items-center justify-center gap-2 hover:bg-primary-container transition-all">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">price_check</span>
